      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to see the logic in fighting it. like, if the end is already decided and it's all just a \"meaningless drag\" as you say... it feels like the most rational thing would be to just stop. if the struggle is the only thing that actually hurts, why keep choosing to feel it?",
